{"content":"<div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-50 to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8 border border-cyan-200\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-4\">❄️ The North: Canada's Last Frontier for Business</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-cyan-800 text-lg leading-relaxed\">\n            Operating in <strong>Yukon, NWT, or Nunavut </strong> comes with unique challenges—and unique funding. \n          The federal government, through <strong> CanNor </strong>, and territorial governments pour money into the North to diversify the economy beyond mining.\n    </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6\">🏛️ CanNor: The Federal Engine </h2>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-lg mb-6\">\n            The <strong> Canadian Northern Economic Development Agency(CanNor) </strong> is the Regional Development Agency for the territories. Their flagship is <strong>IDEANorth</strong>.\n      </p>\n\n                <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-3\"> IDEANorth </h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\"> The main community and business development fund.</p>\n                                <ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2\">\n                                    <li>✅ Funds foundational infrastructure(e.g., community freezers, tourism facilities) </li>\n                                        <li>✅ Sector development(e.g., arts & crafts marketing, tourism capacity) </li>\n                                            <li>✅ Available to businesses, non - profits, and Indigenous organizations </li>\n                                                </ul>\n                                                </div>\n                                                <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm\">\n                                                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-yellow-900 mb-3\"> NHEI(Northern Hydrocarbon Energy Initiative) </h3>\n                                                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\"> Helping the North get off diesel.</p>\n                                                            <ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2\">\n                                                                <li>✅ Renewable energy installations </li>\n                                                                    <li>✅ Energy efficiency retrofits </li>\n                                                                        <li>✅ Biomass, solar, and wind projects </li>\n                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                            </div>\n                                                                            </div>\n\n                                                                            <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6\">🏔️ Yukon: The EDF </h2>\n                                                                                <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-lg mb-6\">\n                                                                                    The <strong> Yukon Economic Development Fund(EDF) </strong> is one of the most flexible funds in the North.\n                                                                                        </p>\n                                                                                        <div class=\"bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-10\">\n                                                                                            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-2\"> EDF Highlights </h3>\n                                                                                                <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-purple-800 space-y-2\">\n                                                                                                    <li><strong>Strategic Industries: </strong> Mining, Film, and Tourism are priorities</li>\n                                                                                                        <li><strong>Tech: </strong> <strong>TechYukon</strong> provides marketing and export support for digital businesses </li>\n                                                                                                            <li> <strong>Flexibility: </strong> Can cover equipment, training, and even travel costs</li>\n                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                                                                                                </div>\n\n                                                                                                                <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6\">🏜️ NWT: SEED Policy </h2>\n                                                                                                                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-lg mb-6\">\n                                                                                                                        The <strong> SEED Policy </strong> (Support for Entrepreneurs and Economic Development) is the NWT's main small business program.\n                                                                                                                            </p>\n                                                                                                                            <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200\">\n                                                                                                                                <div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-orange-600 mb-2\"> Up to $30,000 </div>\n                                                                                                                                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\"> In grants for equipment, marketing, and operational costs.</p>\n                                                                                                                                        <div class=\"bg-orange-50 p-3 rounded text-sm text-orange-800\">\n                                                                                                                                            <strong>Warning: </strong> SEED is first-come, first-served. Apply in April (start of fiscal year) before the budget runs out.\n                                                                                                                                                </div>\n                                                                                                                                                </div>\n\n                                                                                                                                                <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6\">🐻‍❄️ Nunavut: NDC & SIP </h2>\n                                                                                                                                                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-lg mb-6\">\n                                                                                                                                                        The <strong> Nunavut Development Corporation(NDC) </strong> invests equity in businesses that create jobs for Nunavummiut.\n                                                                                                                                                            </p>\n                                                                                                                                                            <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-700 list-disc list-inside bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-10\">\n                                                                                                                                                                <li>The <strong> Strategic Investments Program(SIP) </strong> offers grants for startups and expansions.</li>\n                                                                                                                                                                    <li>Priority is given to Inuit - owned businesses.</li>\n                                                                                                                                                                        <li> Focus on local job creation and community benefit.</li>\n                                                                                                                                                                            </ul>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                            <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6\">❓ Frequently Asked Questions </h2>\n                                                                                                                                                                                <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                    <details class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm group\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                        <summary class=\"flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-bold text-gray-900\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                            Is SEED funding available year - round ?\n                                                                                                                                                                                                <span class=\"text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform\">▼</span>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                    </summary>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                    <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                        Yes, but it's <strong>first-come, first-served</strong>. The budget often runs out by late fall, so apply early in the fiscal year (April 1st).\n                                                                                                                                                                                                            </p>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                            </details>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                            <details class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm group\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                <summary class=\"flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-bold text-gray-900\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Do I need an Indigenous partner ?\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                        <span class=\"text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform\">▼</span>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                            </summary>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Not strictly for all grants, but for major projects(especially on Indigenous land), a <strong> Joint Venture(JV) </strong> with an Indigenous Development Corporation is highly advantageous.\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    </p>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    </details>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <details class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm group\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        <summary class=\"flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-bold text-gray-900\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            What about the high cost of energy ?\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                <span class=\"text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform\">▼</span>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    </summary>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Look into the <strong> Arctic Energy Fund </strong>. It helps businesses and communities switch from diesel to solar, wind, or biomass heating.\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            </p>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            </details>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            </div>"}